				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-muted);">Drawn to art and slow reflection? <a href="#nouwen" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Nouwen</a>. Ready to live as a son or daughter? <a href="#jordan" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Jordan</a>. Whichever you choose, pair it with Scripture &mdash; the prodigal&rsquo;s homecoming in <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/luke/15" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Luke 15</a> is the Father heart of God in a single story.</p>

